lead_paragraph: Tyrone Willingham will return next season as Washington’s coach. The university confirmed the decision at Willingham’s end-of-season news conference. The briefing had been delayed amid speculation that Mark Emmert, the university’s president, was considering whether to fire Willingham, who is 11-25 in his three seasons.
